high_descs: Turn to face the cabinets on your left.
Open the lower left cabinet and take out the purple cloth.
Go to the sink on your left.
Rinse off the cloth in the sink.
Turn around and go to the bath tub.
Put the cloth in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed cloth in the bath tub.

high_descs: Move to the cabinet to the right of the sink
Pick up a rag from the cabinet and close the door
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean the rag in the sink and pick it back up
Move to the tub behind you
Place the rag in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put a clean rag in the tub from one of the cabinets.

high_descs: Turn left and look down to face the lower cabinets.
Open the lower cabinet door furthest to the right and remove the dirty purple rag.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the dirty purple rag in the sink, then turn the water on, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean purple rag.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk over to the tub.
Place the clean purple rag into the middle of the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean purple rag in the tub.
